articles.author: Matt Kyle
articles.title: Southwest plane hit by gunfire at Dallas Love Field - The Dallas Morning News
articles.description: A Southwest Airlines flight from Dallas Love Field to Indianapolis had to be deplaned after the plane was struck by gunfire Friday night.
articles.content:
A Southwest Airlines plane preparing to take off from Dallas Love Field was struck by gunfire Friday night.
Dallas police responded to a shooting call at about 9:50 p.m. at Love Field.
